      "span_text": "The following antibodies were used for immunohistochemistry: antihuman IL-23p19 as published before, [CITATION_1] antihuman IL23p19 (R&D Systems, Minneapolis, Minn), antihuman CD3, antihuman CD68 (DAKO, Hamburg, Germany), antihuman CD3 phycoerythrin (Beckman Coulter, Fullerton, Calif ), antihuman CD68 phycoerythrin (BD Biosciences, San Jose, Calif ), and swine antirabbit IgG fluorescein isothiocyanate (DAKO).",
